2173
01:42:16,830 --> 01:42:18,830
I'll ask all the main questions.

2174
01:42:18,830 --> 01:42:21,000
Either way, the questions we ask
have to change...

2175
01:42:21,000 --> 01:42:22,500
- according to the answers we get.
- Right.

2176
01:42:23,410 --> 01:42:25,810
We should ask a ton of questions.

2177
01:42:25,810 --> 01:42:28,210
- Right.
- All kinds of them.

2178
01:42:28,640 --> 01:42:30,480
But if too many people line up,

2179
01:42:30,480 --> 01:42:33,320
- it's going to take a while.
- No, listen.

2180
01:42:33,680 --> 01:42:35,580
Here's the problem with the others.

2181
01:42:36,180 --> 01:42:38,950
The questioner's time increases, right?

2182
01:42:39,120 --> 01:42:40,760
- That doesn't matter to us.
- True.

2183
01:42:40,760 --> 01:42:42,090
- They...
- But it matters to them.

2184
01:42:42,090 --> 01:42:44,290
- Who will get eliminated.
- Right.

2185
01:42:44,530 --> 01:42:48,500
I'm sure they'll split up the questions.

2186
01:42:48,500 --> 01:42:50,970
In short, the questioner...

2187
01:42:51,330 --> 01:42:53,640
