2188
01:42:53,640 --> 01:42:54,740
- And...
- Okay.

2189
01:42:54,740 --> 01:42:57,510
When you come in 1st or 2nd place,

2190
01:42:57,610 --> 01:42:59,770
the whole team
gets an elimination immunity pass.

2191
01:42:59,770 --> 01:43:01,510
But if one player asks too many questions,

2192
01:43:01,510 --> 01:43:03,040
accumulates too much time,

2193
01:43:03,040 --> 01:43:04,680
