2524
01:55:18,250 --> 01:55:19,710
Everyone was...

2525
01:55:20,010 --> 01:55:21,680
lining up in front of the Voting Room...

2526
01:55:21,680 --> 01:55:23,380
as if waiting to buy a Dubai chewy cookie.

2527
01:55:23,950 --> 01:55:27,560
Just when we were deciding
which questions to ask,

2528
01:55:28,290 --> 01:55:30,930
