Yes, that is correct.

4248
03:09:42,610 --> 03:09:45,480
Was Steve a stuntman?

4249
03:09:48,750 --> 03:09:49,850
Yes, that is correct.

4250
03:09:52,080 --> 03:09:54,680
- Let's ask about this now.
- About what?

4251
03:09:54,880 --> 03:09:56,050
He was a stuntman.

4252
03:09:56,050 --> 03:09:57,420
- That means there was the main actor.
- Right.

4253
03:09:57,420 --> 03:10:00,220
The killer might've wanted to kill
that actor,

4254
03:10:00,420 --> 03:10:02,130
but it was Steve that got killed instead.

4255
03:10:02,960 --> 03:10:04,360
- That's a nice one.
- Right.

4256
03:10:08,130 --> 03:10:11,000
Was the motorcycle defect
caused to harm someone?

4257
03:10:12,070 --> 03:10:13,340
Yes, that is correct.

4258
03:10:15,310 --> 03:10:18,040
Was the motorcycle defect
caused to kill someone?

4259
03:10:20,080 --> 03:10:21,480
Yes, that is correct.

4260
03:10:22,580 --> 03:10:23,710
Was Steve...

4261
03:10:24,650 --> 03:10:28,320
the stand-in for the actor...

4262
03:10:28,720 --> 03:10:32,720
that the one who caused
the motorcycle defect wanted to kill?

4263
03:10:35,860 --> 03:10:37,160
Yes, that is correct.

4264
03:10:37,790 --> 03:10:40,760
After taking the lead,

4265
03:10:40,760 --> 03:10:42,370
it felt like the game had finally started.

4266
03:10:42,500 --> 03:10:45,670
If I calmly narrow things down like this,

4267
03:10:46,040 --> 03:10:47,300
I will take first place no matter what.

4268
03:10:47,340 --> 03:10:48,340
(Round 2 keywords)

4269
03:10:48,340 --> 03:10:52,410
(Stuntman, filming)

4270
03:10:53,140 --> 03:10:54,740
The Time Room is now open.

4271
03:10:55,310 --> 03:10:57,750
The first image hint is revealed.

4272
03:10:58,150 --> 03:10:59,180
Gosh!

4273
03:11:00,280 --> 03:11:01,820
(Team C's Kim Nam Hee and Kim You Hyun...)

4274
03:11:01,820 --> 03:11:04,250
(and Team P2's Lee Jin Hyeong
head out first.)

4275
03:11:04,250 --> 03:11:05,290
Gosh!

4276
03:11:10,790 --> 03:11:13,000
Is that how you're going to be?
I even gave you candy.

4277
03:11:15,370 --> 03:11:16,500
Gosh, I'm so exhausted.

4278
03:11:28,910 --> 03:11:30,250
Writing is prohibited...

4279
03:11:30,250 --> 03:11:31,920
- in the Time Room.
- Should I leave it here?

4280
03:11:32,080 --> 03:11:33,980
Your individual time will get accumulated
twice as fast.

4281
03:11:33,980 --> 03:11:35,350
- Will you enter?
- Yes.

4282
03:11:35,490 --> 03:11:37,490
Jeon Keun Woo has entered.

4283
03:11:37,490 --> 03:11:39,360
Kim You Hyun has entered.

4284
03:11:39,560 --> 03:11:41,660
Lee Jin Hyeong has entered the Time Room.

4285
03:11:42,390 --> 03:11:45,130
(First image hint)

4286
03:11:53,970 --> 03:11:55,570
There was a neat bed...

4287
03:11:56,140 --> 03:11:57,670
and a bag placed next to it.

4288
03:11:57,940 --> 03:11:58,940
There were dumbbells.

4289
03:11:59,910 --> 03:12:04,310
It felt like a neat place...

4290
03:12:05,080 --> 03:12:07,080
of a young man who exercised often.

4291
03:12:07,280 --> 03:12:08,650
(Surprised)

4292
03:12:10,720 --> 03:12:11,990
What can I get from that?

4293
03:12:13,460 --> 03:12:14,490
I felt lost.

4294
03:12:21,970 --> 03:12:25,470
I wondered what I could tell the others.

4295
03:12:28,340 --> 03:12:31,440
(He returns to the main hall.)

4296
03:12:33,110 --> 03:12:35,550
- The bed was really neat.
- Right.

4297
03:12:35,550 --> 03:12:36,550
- The bed.
- Right.

4298
03:12:36,550 --> 03:12:37,850
There was a bag on the floor.

4299
03:12:37,850 --> 03:12:39,850
- The bag was also very neat.
- Right.

4300
03:12:40,020 --> 03:12:43,720
There was a calendar.

4301
03:12:43,720 --> 03:12:47,060
It's the 8th, right?
It's another 2 weeks after that.

4302
03:12:47,060 --> 03:12:48,730
It was delayed by a day.

4303
03:12:48,730 --> 03:12:50,060
I don't get it.

4304
03:12:50,130 --> 03:12:51,900
I think it's a specific date.

4305
03:12:52,200 --> 03:12:53,430
- Right.
- Let's see.

4306
03:12:53,630 --> 03:12:56,230
- I'll check out the image myself.
- Let's see.

4307
03:12:56,230 --> 03:12:58,000
Keun Woo should describe what he saw.

4308
03:12:58,000 --> 03:13:00,440
If our turn comes,
carry on with the questions.

4309
03:13:00,640 --> 03:13:01,910
It's empty.

4310
03:13:02,670 --> 03:13:04,310
This day was skipped.

4311
03:13:04,310 --> 03:13:06,410
There's a gap in between.

4312
03:13:06,640 --> 03:13:08,080
Did you not see the date?

4313
03:13:08,080 --> 03:13:10,410
I don't think it will have
that much of a significance.

4314
03:13:10,410 --> 03:13:13,250
Something must've happened
in between this gap.

4315
03:13:14,920 --> 03:13:19,090
(Team P1's Lee Tae Gyun
came to see the image hint.)

4316
03:13:20,820 --> 03:13:25,030
There were circles around
2, 9, 17, and 24.

4317
03:13:25,300 --> 03:13:27,460
The date of Steve's death was revealed...

4318
03:13:27,660 --> 03:13:30,470
and certain dates were revealed
on the calendar.

4319
03:13:30,470 --> 03:13:32,200
I was certain that
the dates meant something.

4320
03:13:32,200 --> 03:13:34,240
I felt the need to ask about these dates.

4321
03:13:35,510 --> 03:13:37,470
(While Tae Gyun went to
check out the hint)

4322
03:13:37,470 --> 03:13:40,580
Last June,

4323
03:13:40,910 --> 03:13:43,380
there was a riot in the US.

4324
03:13:43,380 --> 03:13:47,250
"Is the country of this incident..."

4325
03:13:48,050 --> 03:13:49,520
"not Korea?"

4326
03:13:49,850 --> 03:13:51,390
- "Is it the US?"
- The US?

4327
03:13:51,390 --> 03:13:53,020
- That was where the riot happened.
- Right.

4328
03:13:53,860 --> 03:13:56,690
Is the country of this incident...

4329
03:13:58,830 --> 03:13:59,930
the US?

4330
03:14:00,460 --> 03:14:01,730
It is not important.

4331
03:14:02,100 --> 03:14:03,800
Then this must be it. Listen.

4332
03:14:04,130 --> 03:14:05,170
This one...

4333
03:14:06,370 --> 03:14:08,370
- has to take medicine.
- Right, medicine.

4334
03:14:08,370 --> 03:14:10,410
But the doctor has to...

4335
03:14:10,440 --> 03:14:12,380
prescribe once every two weeks.

4336
03:14:12,540 --> 03:14:14,440
But as for the medicine...

4337
03:14:14,440 --> 03:14:16,750
It wasn't intentional for the doctor
to prescribe it wrong.

4338
03:14:16,980 --> 03:14:19,420
Why don't we ask if they have
any chronic health conditions?

4339
03:14:19,850 --> 03:14:22,550
Did Steve have to take medicine...

4340
03:14:22,550 --> 03:14:27,190
on designated dates
due to his chronic health condition?

4341
03:14:27,520 --> 03:14:29,560
No, that is incorrect.

4342
03:14:30,660 --> 03:14:33,860
Did Steve have a mission...

4343
03:14:33,860 --> 03:14:37,170
that he had to complete
on designated dates?

4344
03:14:37,430 --> 03:14:39,370
No, that is incorrect.

4345
03:14:39,640 --> 03:14:41,170
We're done for.

4346
03:14:43,240 --> 03:14:45,680
I asked these questions, and she said no.

4347
03:14:46,140 --> 03:14:47,380
"Did Steve have a mission..."

4348
03:14:47,380 --> 03:14:48,580
"that he had to complete
on designated dates?"

4349
03:14:48,580 --> 03:14:49,610
And she said no.

4350
03:14:49,810 --> 03:14:52,120
(Sighing)

4351
03:14:52,680 --> 03:14:53,720
Darn it.

4352
03:14:57,320 --> 03:14:58,890
They made it so tricky.

4353
03:15:00,290 --> 03:15:02,990
We even talked about Steve being a mafia.

4354
03:15:02,990 --> 03:15:04,690
Because Steve is a mafia,

4355
03:15:04,690 --> 03:15:07,030
he got killed
while trying to transport drugs.

4356
03:15:07,330 --> 03:15:08,430
We came up with all sorts of theories,

4357
03:15:08,430 --> 03:15:11,430
him being shot by a gun too.

4358
03:15:11,570 --> 03:15:14,570
This is where it got really hard.

4359
03:15:14,570 --> 03:15:18,340
I was just so frustrated.

4360
03:15:18,680 --> 03:15:20,110
No way.

4361
03:15:20,110 --> 03:15:22,450
(Lee Jin Hyeong of P2
returns after seeing the image hint.)

4362
03:15:22,450 --> 03:15:24,210
I'll tell you what the image was.

4363
03:15:24,550 --> 03:15:25,680
It's someone's room.

4364
03:15:25,820 --> 03:15:27,620
The first hint was revealed,

4365
03:15:27,620 --> 03:15:28,820
so I rushed over.

4366
03:15:28,820 --> 03:15:31,020
Certain dates on the calendar are circled,

4367
03:15:31,020 --> 03:15:32,660
and there wasn't one on June 12.

4368
03:15:32,660 --> 03:15:34,390
There were dumbbells and a bench.

4369
03:15:34,390 --> 03:15:36,260
It was obviously a stuntman's room.

4370
03:15:36,260 --> 03:15:39,160
This guy had no shoot on June 12.

4371
03:15:39,160 --> 03:15:40,530
Our prediction was right.

4372
03:15:41,000 --> 03:15:43,070
June 2, 9, 12, 24.

4373
03:15:43,130 --> 03:15:44,570
- Okay.
- Those were circled?

4374
03:15:44,570 --> 03:15:46,370
No, on June 12,

4375
03:15:46,370 --> 03:15:47,640
he had no schedule.

4376
03:15:47,640 --> 03:15:50,210
There are many dumbbells in the room
and a bench.

4377
03:15:50,210 --> 03:15:51,410
- It's obviously a stuntman's room.
- That's right.

4378
03:15:51,410 --> 03:15:53,040
It was a hint to show that.

4379
03:15:53,040 --> 03:15:54,040
- Bench and dumbbells.
- Hey.

4380
03:15:54,040 --> 03:15:55,950
But we found that out first.

4381
03:15:55,950 --> 03:15:57,810
- That's right. It's a bit of a shame.
- It's a shame.

4382
03:15:57,880 --> 03:15:59,350
- We found that out right away.
- I know.

4383
03:15:59,650 --> 03:16:01,220
The Time Room is open.

4384
03:16:01,220 --> 03:16:03,550
The second image hint is revealed.

4385
03:16:08,620 --> 03:16:11,290
Lee Tae Gyun has entered the Time Room.

4386
03:16:11,290 --> 03:16:12,700
(Lee Tae Gyun of P1
has entered the Time Room.)

4387
03:16:12,700 --> 03:16:13,900
Who is this jerk?

4388
03:16:19,470 --> 03:16:22,740
(The second image hint)

4389
03:16:23,770 --> 03:16:28,040
A man in a helmet dressed in black...

4390
03:16:28,040 --> 03:16:30,250
was wrapping his arm
around the woman's waist.

4391
03:16:31,210 --> 03:16:33,880
There was a hand...

4392
03:16:33,880 --> 03:16:36,350
of someone else taking a photo of that.

4393
03:16:37,020 --> 03:16:41,420
But the woman's gaze
and the way she looks at him...

4394
03:16:42,290 --> 03:16:45,130
felt like she was anxious.

4395
03:16:45,130 --> 03:16:46,430
As though she didn't like him.

4396
03:16:46,430 --> 03:16:48,300
And his face...

4397
03:16:48,300 --> 03:16:49,930
was covered by a helmet,

4398
03:16:49,930 --> 03:16:53,570
so I couldn't tell if it was Steve or not.

4399
03:16:53,570 --> 03:16:55,740
I thought I should figure that out.

4400
03:16:56,710 --> 03:16:58,410
(Kim Nam Hee of Team C
returns after checking the hint.)

4401
03:16:58,410 --> 03:16:59,740
I'll tell you.

4402
03:17:00,480 --> 03:17:02,280
The photo was taken with a phone,

4403
03:17:02,280 --> 03:17:03,650
and the glove is Steve's.

4404
03:17:03,650 --> 03:17:05,350
It's a glove that shows fingers.

4405
03:17:05,350 --> 03:17:07,380
- From the photo...
- The one holding the phone?

4406
03:17:07,380 --> 03:17:08,920
- Yes.
- I see.

4407
03:17:08,920 --> 03:17:12,260
The actor is wearing
the same leather jacket,

4408
03:17:12,260 --> 03:17:14,420
but his gloves cover all the fingers.

4409
03:17:15,060 --> 03:17:16,160
But Steve's gloves don't.

4410
03:17:16,330 --> 03:17:18,560
So Steve is the one who took the photo.

4411
03:17:18,560 --> 03:17:21,230
Since I majored in fashion,
I take a careful look at clothes.

4412
03:17:21,230 --> 03:17:23,730
I tend to remember
what someone is wearing.

4413
03:17:23,730 --> 03:17:26,000
I scanned
what Steve was wearing at once...

4414
03:17:26,170 --> 03:17:27,400
and went to see the image hint.

4415
03:17:29,270 --> 03:17:31,270
From the second image hint,

4416
03:17:31,270 --> 03:17:33,210
I could see that the man holding
the camera was in Steve's glove.

4417
03:17:33,210 --> 03:17:35,980
It's a leather glove,

4418
03:17:35,980 --> 03:17:38,310
but it was fingerless.

4419
03:17:39,020 --> 03:17:41,480
(The same person with the same glove?)

4420
03:17:41,620 --> 03:17:44,590
The man in the photo
in a leather jacket...

4421
03:17:44,590 --> 03:17:47,020
was dressed like Steve
but with a helmet on.

4422
03:17:47,020 --> 03:17:50,990
The man whose face wasn't revealed
had gloves...

4423
03:17:50,990 --> 03:17:52,200
with full fingers.

4424
03:17:52,200 --> 03:17:54,530
It was a full-finger leather glove.

4425
03:17:54,530 --> 03:17:57,130
I thought the one taking the photo
was Steve,

4426
03:17:57,130 --> 03:17:59,870
and the person in the photo
must be someone else.

4427
03:18:00,100 --> 03:18:01,670
In the second image hint,

4428
03:18:02,440 --> 03:18:07,280
is the person taking the photo...

4429
03:18:07,440 --> 03:18:08,540
Steve?

4430
03:18:09,280 --> 03:18:10,810
Yes, that is correct.

4431
03:18:11,550 --> 03:18:12,750
In the second image hint,

4432
03:18:13,350 --> 03:18:17,250
is the one in a helmet...

4433
03:18:17,720 --> 03:18:20,290
the actor whom the culprit
tried to kill...

4434
03:18:20,290 --> 03:18:24,190
by tampering with the motorcycle?

4435
03:18:25,290 --> 03:18:27,100
Yes, that is correct.

4436
03:18:27,400 --> 03:18:29,630
After seeing the woman in the second hint,

4437
03:18:29,630 --> 03:18:32,130
a new person appeared.

4438
03:18:32,130 --> 03:18:33,500
I tried to figure out...

4439
03:18:33,500 --> 03:18:35,840
how this person is related
to the rest of them.

4440
03:18:35,840 --> 03:18:37,610
That's what I tried to figure out first.

4441
03:18:37,610 --> 03:18:40,640
Whether the man cheated...

4442
03:18:40,640 --> 03:18:43,910
or if she was not happy with...

4443
03:18:43,910 --> 03:18:45,210
- Right.
- how he behaved...

4444
03:18:45,210 --> 03:18:48,380
She tried to cause
an accident on purpose to kill him,

4445
03:18:48,380 --> 03:18:50,020
- but Steve ended up dying.
- I see.

4446
03:18:50,020 --> 03:18:51,290
He took the photo,

4447
03:18:51,450 --> 03:18:52,860
and some other woman saw it.

4448
03:18:53,820 --> 03:18:57,130
So, maybe he has a wife...

4449
03:18:57,130 --> 03:18:58,860
- or a girlfriend.
- I see. Okay.

4450
03:18:58,860 --> 03:19:01,500
So, she tried to kill him,

4451
03:19:02,130 --> 03:19:03,870
but Steve died instead.

4452
03:19:04,430 --> 03:19:06,840
- That makes sense.
- Yes.

4453
03:19:06,840 --> 03:19:10,170
Then it could be a woman
who caused all this.

4454
03:19:10,170 --> 03:19:11,170
Secondly...

4455
03:19:11,240 --> 03:19:12,640
Was the motorcycle tampered...

4456
03:19:12,810 --> 03:19:15,240
by the woman in the second image hint?

4457
03:19:18,750 --> 03:19:20,550
No, that is incorrect.

4458
03:19:24,420 --> 03:19:25,690
- This isn't the case, then.
- This isn't it?

4459
03:19:27,990 --> 03:19:30,490
- Then this is important.
- This isn't it.

4460
03:19:30,490 --> 03:19:32,830
Then what matters is who did it.

4461
03:19:33,830 --> 03:19:36,270
But I think they set it as a film set...

4462
03:19:36,700 --> 03:19:38,870
to not include a crime of passion.

4463
03:19:38,870 --> 03:19:41,200
There was a crime of passion
in the third season too.

4464
03:19:41,300 --> 03:19:42,670
I don't think it'll be included.

4465
03:19:42,770 --> 03:19:44,410
I'm 100 percent sure...

4466
03:19:44,870 --> 03:19:46,880
that it was a scheme of the rival actor.

4467
03:19:46,980 --> 03:19:48,080
- Right.
- That seems to be most likely.

4468
03:19:48,080 --> 03:19:49,410
- As a cliche.
- In terms of cliche.

4469
03:19:49,610 --> 03:19:52,210
Also, about ex lovers...

4470
03:19:52,210 --> 03:19:53,650
Right. It's too obvious.

4471
03:19:54,180 --> 03:19:56,250
I think the critical focus should be
on cliches.

4472
03:19:56,720 --> 03:20:00,990
I think they create stories
that sound familiar.

4473
03:20:00,990 --> 03:20:04,860
I thought they created stories
that are like movies.

4474
03:20:04,860 --> 03:20:07,730
If you think about the third season,

4475
03:20:08,530 --> 03:20:11,130
there was a story about
a president's assassin...

4476
03:20:11,530 --> 03:20:14,640
and a story about twins' affairs.

4477
03:20:15,500 --> 03:20:16,740
Also, Mark had to die...

4478
03:20:18,310 --> 03:20:22,480
because of the man
he killed ten years ago.

4479
03:20:22,750 --> 03:20:24,480
He died of poisonous gas.

4480
03:20:24,480 --> 03:20:26,020
That's totally like a movie.

4481
03:20:26,020 --> 03:20:28,820
I thought, "Then I should come up..."

4482
03:20:28,820 --> 03:20:30,220
"with a cliche that I might see
in a movie."

4483
03:20:30,350 --> 03:20:31,650
I think it's about rivalry.

4484
03:20:31,650 --> 03:20:33,090
One that was after the job?

4485
03:20:33,220 --> 03:20:34,720
- Something like that.
- Yes.

4486
03:20:34,720 --> 03:20:36,930
You should ask if the incident
was caused because of the role.

4487
03:20:36,930 --> 03:20:38,290
I think we should ask that first.

4488
03:20:39,930 --> 03:20:42,370
The one who tampered with the engine...

4489
03:20:42,530 --> 03:20:46,670
Was it the rival actor
who was supposed to...

4490
03:20:46,670 --> 03:20:49,310
ride the motorcycle that Steve did?

4491
03:20:51,540 --> 03:20:53,040
No, that is incorrect.

4492
03:20:55,710 --> 03:20:56,710
Darn.

4493
03:20:59,720 --> 03:21:02,320
"What? It's incorrect? That can't be."

4494
03:21:03,150 --> 03:21:04,190
"That can't be."

4495
03:21:04,220 --> 03:21:07,390
Gosh, this isn't as easy as I thought.

4496
03:21:07,890 --> 03:21:09,790
It's true they were after the actor.

4497
03:21:10,130 --> 03:21:11,960
- The role...
- Maybe it's like this.

4498
03:21:11,960 --> 03:21:14,000
It's quite the imagination.

4499
03:21:14,000 --> 03:21:17,430
Say that I'm the nurse of a hospital ward
and I'm a fan of his.

4500
03:21:17,430 --> 03:21:19,970
I wanted to cause an accident
to have him in my ward.

4501
03:21:19,970 --> 03:21:21,070
I could've caused an accident on purpose.

4502
